description: Manage service-side device registrations for an individual enrollment in an Azure IoT Hub Device Provisioning Service.

commands.name: az iot dps enrollment registration delete
commands.summary: Delete a device registration for an individual enrollment in an Azure IoT Hub Device Provisioning Service.
commands.syntax:
az iot dps enrollment registration delete --eid
                                          [--auth-type {key, login}]
                                          [--dps-name]
                                          [--etag]
                                          [--login]
                                          [--resource-group]

commands.name: az iot dps enrollment registration show
commands.summary: Get a device registration for an individual enrollment in an Azure IoT Hub Device Provisioning Service.
commands.syntax:
az iot dps enrollment registration show --eid
                                        [--auth-type {key, login}]
                                        [--dps-name]
                                        [--login]
                                        [--resource-group]
